template(name='home')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    meta(name='description', content='It's not rocket science.  Free-to-play online multiplayer SatNav!')
    meta(name='author', content='Cameron Shiell')
    title SatNav
    // Custom Fonts
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:400,700,400italic,700italic', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    // HTML5 Shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries
    // WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file://
    //if lt IE 9
      script(src='https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js')
      script(src='https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js')
  body
    // Navigation
    nav.navbar.navbar-default.navbar-fixed-top
      .container
        // Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display
        .navbar-header.page-scroll
          button.navbar-toggle(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1')
            span.sr-only Toggle navigation
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar
          a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top') SatNav
          .fb-like(data-href="https://www.facebook.com/roborallyonline", data-layout="button_count", data-action="like", data-show-faces="true", data-share="true")
        // Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling
        #bs-example-navbar-collapse-1.collapse.navbar-collapse
          ul.nav.navbar-nav.navbar-right
            li.hidden
              a(href='#page-top')
            li.page-scroll
              a(href='#online') Play online
            li.page-scroll
              a(href='#about') About
    // Header
    header
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12
            .intro-text
              span.name SatNav
              hr.star-light
              span.skills It's not rocket science.
    // Online Section
    section#online
      .container
        .row
          .col-leg-12.text-center
            h2 Play online
            hr.star-primary
            p
              | Welcome to SatNav online! SatNav online is 100% free to play.
              | SatNav is a fun game full of chaos. It's all about programming your satellites to pass checkpoints and seeing what happens next as they run into each other and lots of obstacles. Tons of fun.
            br
            a(href="{{pathFor 'gamelist.page'}}").btn.btn-primary.btn-xlg Play SatNav online!
            br
    // About Section
    section#about.success
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            h2 About
            hr.star-light
        .row
          .col-lg-4.col-lg-offset-2
            p
              | Imagine that you're controlling a satellite around another planet. Imagine that you can only send instructions for a few seconds each orbit, enough to transmit five simple commands. Your task is to move a satellite to a series of checkpoints. The wrinkle, however, is that the planet's sky is filled with all kinds of inconvenient (if not down-right deadly) obstacles located in various locations, and you're not the only satellite out there so suddenly your perfect route is something less than that..
          .col-lg-4
            p
              | In SatNav players each control a different satellite in a race through a dangerous sky. Several goals will be placed on the board and you must navigate your satellite to them in a specific order. The boards can be combined in several different ways to accommodate different player counts and races can be as long or as short as player's desire.
              | SatNav is a multiplayer turn based strategy game.
    #fb-root
    // Footer
    footer.text-center
      .footer-above
        .container
          .row
              h3 About SatNav.com
              p
                | This is a new game based upon an old codebase, just for fun because we love the game!
      .footer-below
        .container
          .row
            .col-lg-12
              | Copyright Â© SatNav 2017
              a.pull-right(href='https://mixpanel.com/f/partner')
                img(src='https://cdn.mxpnl.com/site_media/images/partner/badge_blue.png' alt='Mobile Analytics')
    // Scroll to Top Button (Only visible on small and extra-small screen sizes)
    .scroll-top.page-scroll.visible-xs.visble-sm
      a.btn.btn-primary(href='#page-top')
        i.fa.fa-chevron-up
